# Ideas

- Patzip: Track Health Conditions by Zip Code

- SafeLabs: Reducing hospital acquired infection

- An app that scans a prescription or medication label and checks for:
Drug interactions
Allergies (based on user profile)
Dosage errors
Features:
Barcode/QR code scanner for medication
Alerts for high-risk medications
Pill reminder for patients to take their medication correctly

